  "body": "<p>Exciting news, friends! <a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">Brave + Bold</a>, my newest collection with American Crafts, is now available to purchase ONLINE! Click the button to <a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">shop the Brave + Bold collection</a> and have a look at some of the fun new scrapbooking supplies and some layouts with the new products below!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n    SHOP NOW\n  </a>\n\n\n\n \n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614923074476-XYDM4QKYZMAM4YG9FQL5/Amy-Tangerine-Brave%2BBold-Vinyl-Stickers.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614923441253-ZVG8W2FWO5S541T6EJ6D/Amy-Tangerine-Brave-and-Bold-Washi-Tape.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Vinyl Stickers and Washi Tape from the Brave and Bold collection by Amy Tangerine</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614923881182-7EZ49V5LYF8UR6ODMVNL/Amy-Tangerine-Bold-Brave-Clear-Acrylic-Stamps.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614924142974-F0782CPMCB5QS3P514PQ/Amy-Tangerine-Sticker-Book-Brave-and-Bold.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Clear Acrylic Stamp Set and Sticker Book</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614924537401-CH72W3XOH4UU4TWPPVRX/Brave-and-Bold-Scrapbook-Paper.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614925789447-8RWPHA3EH2EG1Q50T13K/AT-Brave-Bold-Die-Cuts.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>12x12 Patterned Paper and Die Cuts</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614926024365-04BP3415YG6FEIEKU59N/AT-Brave-Bold-Sticker-Roll.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614926347250-7W7CK9ANLJ7I5MIXZETO/AT-Brave-Bold-Travel-Watercolor-Set.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Sticker Roll and Travel Watercolor Set </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614926634931-2P4XSI0K0BGATC8ZGN1I/Amy-Tangerine-Scrapbook-Layout-Brave-Bold.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1614927045019-SQT30PHJ5RLWDW6JECDW/Amy-Tangerine-Scrapbook-Ideas-Brave-Bold.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>12x12 Scrapbook Layout and Traveler’s Notebook Spread </p><p>Want to see some of the products up close? Watch my YouTube video and see me swatch the new colors in the Travel Watercolor Set!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>I hope you love this new collection as much as I do! I’d love to see what you create with these new goodies from <a href=\"http://bit.ly/sbamy\">Brave + Bold</a>. Tag me Instagram @amytangerine and use #amytangerine and #atbraveandbold! </p>"
